WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.800
SignalForge IQ is built to help users grow from signals to structured automation.

00:00:05.800 --> 00:00:14.400
Phase one starts with manual signals, analytics, and performance tracking.

00:00:14.400 --> 00:00:20.800
You stay in control while learning how the strategy behaves in real market conditions.

00:00:20.800 --> 00:00:29.800
Then Elite unlocks execution-ready automation, starting with controlled signal delivery and supported integrations.

00:00:29.800 --> 00:00:38.500
The first execution integration starts with Alpaca paper trading, so users can test safely before going live.

00:00:38.500 --> 00:00:44.300
From there, supported live execution and advanced routing can be added for users who are ready.

00:00:44.300 --> 00:00:48.000
Start with signals. Upgrade when ready. Automate with control.
